{
  "message": "fix(vercel): simplify install command and add local env to gitignore\n\nThe monorepo build was failing because the install command was trying\nto navigate to the workspace root. This simplifies the Vercel deployment\nby using a direct `bun install` instead of relative path navigation.\n\nChanges:\n- vercel.json: Change installCommand from \"cd ../.. && bun install\" to \"bun install\"\n- .gitignore: Add .env*.local pattern to prevent accidental credential commits\n\nThe root-level vercel.json is added as a convenience copy for deployment reference.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "e3a7542e062e6088092fc56bb344b6555634857a",
      "filename": "apps/web/.gitignore",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 1,
      "deletions": 0,
      "changes": 1,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/Dicklesworthstone/jeffreysprompts.com/blob/deb96dff9d4d51e7340301bd5543355aca1111f1/apps%2Fweb%2F.gitignore",
